author: dweiss
msg: Pass tests.timeoutSuite to junit4 if defined on command line or in user properties. This can be used to lower (or increase) the default timeout value. Example: -Dtests.timeoutSuite=5000! (5 seconds, note the exclamation mark -- this means to override the annotation defaults).
